BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury opposition Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Aries 25°58’) - opposition - Natal Uranus \nYour mind is working at full speed. You will therefore tend to draw conclusions without knowing all the facts. Try to slow down and think carefully first. But it will be challenging for you now, because you will lack patience. You will feel reluctant to perform any boring, repetitive activities. Your ability to look at problems from different perspectives will improve now and it will help you solve them. It is possible that during this transit you will suffer from headaches, anxiety and nervousness.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260501T000100Z
DTEND:20260501T000100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:1_tr_me_op_ur
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus opposition Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Gemini 9°22’) - opposition - Natal Neptune \nYou tend to see things in a better light than they really are. You adjust the reality so that it does not spoil your happiness. This will have a beneficial effect on your mood but avoid dealing with practical issues. Postpone any legal, financial, or formal matters for later.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 9th house: \nThis transit is great for adventures in foreign countries, but also in places where you have never been before. You may be surprised at the beauty of places that are near you but which you have never had time to see. You will have a great time if you go on holiday now.  \nYou will be attracted by independent and entertaining people with whom you can share a lot of unusual experiences. These situations will make you think about how you live your life, and they will show you new viewpoints that you may want to share with others. You may become more interested in other cultures or you may fall in love with a foreigner. You may also meet a teacher, a philosopher, a pilot, a linguist, or an adventurer whom you fall in love with.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260501T213800Z
DTEND:20260501T213800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:2_tr_ve_op_ne
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus opposition Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Gemini 10°13’) - opposition - Natal Moon \nYou will now find it easier to give and receive love. However, be careful not to fulfil the wishes of others that you are not comfortable with. It is a good time for meeting friends and acquaintances because others will think you are very nice and attractive. During this transit any misunderstandings in your romantic relationship will likely be resolved because you will be able to see things very easily from other people´s perspective. However, make sure that your needs and feelings are respected.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 9th house: \nThis transit is great for adventures in foreign countries, but also in places where you have never been before. You may be surprised at the beauty of places that are near you but which you have never had time to see. You will have a great time if you go on holiday now.  \nYou will be attracted by independent and entertaining people with whom you can share a lot of unusual experiences. These situations will make you think about how you live your life, and they will show you new viewpoints that you may want to share with others. You may become more interested in other cultures or you may fall in love with a foreigner. You may also meet a teacher, a philosopher, a pilot, a linguist, or an adventurer whom you fall in love with.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260502T143100Z
DTEND:20260502T143100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:3_tr_ve_op_mo
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury sextile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Aries 29°22’) - sextile - Natal Saturn \nUse your ability to think logically and clearly during this transit. If you are facing problems that require concentration and discipline, it is a good time to begin solving them. Although these activities may not be too much fun, solving them will pay off in the long run. Other people may see you as reserved and quiet because you are too concentrated on practical issues.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260502T191100Z
DTEND:20260502T191100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:4_tr_me_se_sa
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Saturn trine Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Saturn (Aries 9°22’) - trine - Natal Neptune \nYour material and spiritual needs are now balanced, and they are moving you forward. You may now begin transforming your life for the better. It is also a great time to practice yoga and study subjects that involve mysticism.  \n \nTransit Saturn in Natal 6th house: \nThis transit may bring health problems that will point out things that need to be changed. Mostly they will not be serious, and you will overcome them easily. You should especially evaluate your daily routine, habits and lifestyle. It is an ideal opportunity to get rid of unhealthy habits and replace them with good habits, for example with regular exercise. You may experience a stressful period at work because you will have too many duties. Try to eliminate stress by bringing order and organizing your work better. This will increase your work efficiency, which in turn will reduce your stress. If you manage the lessons of this transit correctly, you will be more vital, productive, healthier, and focused at work.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260503T015300Z
DTEND:20260503T015300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:5_tr_sa_tr_ne
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury sextile Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Taurus 4°24’) - sextile - Natal Venus \nYou can easily meet new acquaintances and establish new relationships. Existing relationships, especially romantic relationships, can reach a new level or resolve their issues. This transit is favourable period for negotiating, presenting your thoughts and ideas, public relations and business meetings. You will do very well in these areas because you will be very charming and diplomatic. You can also expect good news.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260505T085800Z
DTEND:20260505T085800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:6_tr_me_se_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars conjunction Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Aries 20°41’) - conjunction - Natal Sun \nYou will be assertive and confident. You will not have a problem taking initiative. However, do not throw yourself impulsively into things without thinking first. You will have the need to keep busy all the time and to be everywhere. There may be some tension in the relationship with your superiors or your father. Try to get rid of excess energy by doing some contact sports or activities that require competitiveness. \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit will try to teach you the importance of compromise. Try to avoid unnecessary conflicts with your partner and realize that two people are better off when they work together. Your partner, friend or business partner will now require more attention than usual. This can lead to feelings of frustration stemming from losing free time. However, you will still be happy about your relationship and think about whether it is time to move your relationship to the next level. If you have feared the commitment, you will be more optimistic about it now. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
