SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury sextile Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Taurus 7°26’) - sextile - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit is favourable for trips, any type of learning and education, writing, and relationships with the public and lawyers. Your mind is overflowing with optimism, and it is easy for other people to work with you. You may be promoted at work or you may receive an interesting offer.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit is great for private conversations. It is therefore an ideal time to try to resolve any problems that you may have with your partner. Even with your business partners you will get along extremely well. However, you will feel uncomfortable in larger groups of people and you will lack assertiveness. You will feel better in the role of negotiator and compromise maker. You will be very charming, which will make it easier for you to accomplish your goals. It is a good time for deep conversations and debates, including those on controversial topics. However, if there is a combination with difficult aspects, you should be cautious about problems in communication with your loved ones.   \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
