SUMMARY:Tr. Saturn trine Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Saturn (Aries 10°13’) - trine - Natal Moon \nYou will use more logic and you will be more emotionally balanced. It is therefore a good time to make decisions and address important issues. During this transit you will be able to cope with all your responsibilities and deal with every problem you face.  \n \nTransit Saturn in Natal 6th house: \nThis transit may bring health problems that will point out things that need to be changed. Mostly they will not be serious, and you will overcome them easily. You should especially evaluate your daily routine, habits and lifestyle. It is an ideal opportunity to get rid of unhealthy habits and replace them with good habits, for example with regular exercise. You may experience a stressful period at work because you will have too many duties. Try to eliminate stress by bringing order and organizing your work better. This will increase your work efficiency, which in turn will reduce your stress. If you manage the lessons of this transit correctly, you will be more vital, productive, healthier, and focused at work.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
