BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Jupiter square Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Jupiter (Cancer 20°41’) - square - Natal Sun \nYou may be overly optimistic, self-confident, lazy and reluctant to do anything. Beware of making bad decisions and wasting energy or money on unnecessary things. During this transit Jupiter is checking your ego.  \n \nTransit Jupiter in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit is good for your career. It can bring promotion, increased productivity, better qualifications and success in your business. Sometimes it can also mean marriage because it is associated with a general improvement of your status. You will also have more freedom when you do your work. To maximize your success, you should approach things and people with sincerity and integrity. This will allow people in senior positions and in authority to be more inclined to positively respond to your requests. If Jupiter forms negative aspects, beware of abuse of power and prestige, selfishness and arrogance.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
