SUMMARY:Tr. Mars sextile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Aries 29°22’) - sextile - Natal Saturn \nHonest and diligent effort will bring you results. You will be more patient and willing to wait for the fruits of your labor. In your work you will be methodical and strategic, and you will not make even the slightest mistakes. This transit is especially useful when your work involves analysis.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit will try to teach you the importance of compromise. Try to avoid unnecessary conflicts with your partner and realize that two people are better off when they work together. Your partner, friend or business partner will now require more attention than usual. This can lead to feelings of frustration stemming from losing free time. However, you will still be happy about your relationship and think about whether it is time to move your relationship to the next level. If you have feared the commitment, you will be more optimistic about it now. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
