BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Gemini 7°26’) - square - Natal Jupiter \nYou will tend to exaggerate and be too idealistic. You may miss an important detail in your life or at work. Try not to be overly optimistic now - be realistic and keep your feet on the ground.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit you will be absorbed in deep thoughts and you will be very intuitive.  \nYou will be able to uncover the hidden meanings of the words spoken by people around you and their hidden motives. Your intuition will guide you and show you who you can trust and who you should be careful with. This intuition also helps you in financial planning.  \nAs the 8th house is associated with hidden, tabooed things, you will easily deal with intimate and sensitive things, which would at other times cause controversy. Occult sciences, sex, forbidden topics - all these will attract you. Especially death and afterlife are topics you will often think about now. In exceptional cases, you may be a target of investigations during this period.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260520T205800Z
DTEND:20260520T205800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:23_tr_me_sq_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury opposition Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Gemini 9°22’) - opposition - Natal Neptune \nBeware of losing touch with reality as a result of excessive daydreaming. Your decision-making ability will also be affected, so make sure you are able to separate facts from fiction and that you have truthful information. It is not a good time to negotiate and practice professions requiring attention to detail (like accounting or programming). The best way to enjoy this transit is to go to a cultural event such as concert, a theatre play or a museum.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260521T184800Z
DTEND:20260521T184800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:24_tr_me_op_ne
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury opposition Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Gemini 10°13’) - opposition - Natal Moon \nThis transit can be a messenger of bad news. It also indicates an imbalance between your emotional and rational side. You may feel frustrated when talking to other people because you will not feel understood. You can also take the opinions of other people too seriously, especially if the conversation revolves around your home and family affairs. You should therefore avoid excessive hypersensitivity because it will help you avoid arguments.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 9th house: \nNow is one of the best times for studying and career development. If you want to enrol in a university or start looking for a new job, do it now!  \nNow you are a great storyteller and other people will love listening to your stories. You can fully use your creativity when writing, learning and communicating with people, especially those from university environment and from other cultures. Now you can also learn new languages with ease. Overall, you will be tolerant of alternative views, ideas and thoughts. It is also possible that you will get a great new idea that will bring you success.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260522T042900Z
DTEND:20260522T042900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:25_tr_me_op_mo
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus trine Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Cancer 4°24’) - trine - Natal Venus \nYou will spend time in a pleasant company of other people, and it is highly unlikely that you will be involved in any misunderstandings and quarrels. You will be in a great mood, which will increase your popularity. You may gain large sums of money from your investments.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 9th house: \nThis transit is great for adventures in foreign countries, but also in places where you have never been before. You may be surprised at the beauty of places that are near you but which you have never had time to see. You will have a great time if you go on holiday now.  \nYou will be attracted by independent and entertaining people with whom you can share a lot of unusual experiences. These situations will make you think about how you live your life, and they will show you new viewpoints that you may want to share with others. You may become more interested in other cultures or you may fall in love with a foreigner. You may also meet a teacher, a philosopher, a pilot, a linguist, or an adventurer whom you fall in love with.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260522T174900Z
DTEND:20260522T174900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:26_tr_ve_tr_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus square Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Cancer 5°03’) - square - Natal Pluto \nWith this transit you will feel all the emotions more intensely. Any emotions will now be harder to ignore - whether positive or negative. Control your reactions, they may be too intense or too aggressive. You may also be easily manipulated or seduced by other people. You will think more about what relationships are good for you, or what kind of behaviour you don’t want to tolerate. This transformation aspect will also apply to your character. You should therefore use this transit to achieve positive changes, be it positive changes in you or in others.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 9th house: \nThis transit is great for adventures in foreign countries, but also in places where you have never been before. You may be surprised at the beauty of places that are near you but which you have never had time to see. You will have a great time if you go on holiday now.  \nYou will be attracted by independent and entertaining people with whom you can share a lot of unusual experiences. These situations will make you think about how you live your life, and they will show you new viewpoints that you may want to share with others. You may become more interested in other cultures or you may fall in love with a foreigner. You may also meet a teacher, a philosopher, a pilot, a linguist, or an adventurer whom you fall in love with.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260523T064200Z
DTEND:20260523T064200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:27_tr_ve_sq_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars sextile Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Taurus 4°24’) - sextile - Natal Venus \nYou will feel the desire to follow your heart. You will be guided by what seems right to you. However, be aware that your evaluations are now based on your emotions. Whether it is a person, thing or opportunity, you will do all you can to get it. However, do not forget to enjoy life.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit will try to teach you the importance of compromise. Try to avoid unnecessary conflicts with your partner and realize that two people are better off when they work together. Your partner, friend or business partner will now require more attention than usual. This can lead to feelings of frustration stemming from losing free time. However, you will still be happy about your relationship and think about whether it is time to move your relationship to the next level. If you have feared the commitment, you will be more optimistic about it now. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260524T193500Z
DTEND:20260524T193500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:28_tr_ma_se_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus trine Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Cancer 7°26’) - trine - Natal Jupiter \nThis transit will make you feel happy and satisfied. You will enjoy even the slightest pleasure and pass this feeling on to others. Nothing will upset you. You may also feel a bit lazy and seek pleasure. Your relationships will flourish. In the area of finance, you may make a good investment, or you may get a great opportunity to acquire finances. If you are dealing with legal issues, this transit will contribute to a satisfactory outcome. It is a great time for social events, excursions or a vacation.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 9th house: \nThis transit is great for adventures in foreign countries, but also in places where you have never been before. You may be surprised at the beauty of places that are near you but which you have never had time to see. You will have a great time if you go on holiday now.  \nYou will be attracted by independent and entertaining people with whom you can share a lot of unusual experiences. These situations will make you think about how you live your life, and they will show you new viewpoints that you may want to share with others. You may become more interested in other cultures or you may fall in love with a foreigner. You may also meet a teacher, a philosopher, a pilot, a linguist, or an adventurer whom you fall in love with.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260525T065800Z
DTEND:20260525T065800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:29_tr_ve_tr_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun square Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Gemini 4°24’) - square - Natal Venus \nIt’s time to think about your relationships and whether they give you what you need. If you are dissatisfied, it is time for change, especially if you feel that it is mostly you who gives in the relationship. Be careful not to spend too much money on other people and that you do not use shopping to make you feel better when you are dissatisfied. Beware of laziness and vanity. \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 8th house: \nIt’s time for changes! This transit brings with it a profound transformation and it will shine light on everything hidden.  \nIf you are not satisfied with any aspect of life, it is the ideal time to reflect on it and get rid of things that are not for your benefit. It can be people who influence you, your negative qualities and habits, or material things. This transformation is necessary and will provide space for the emergence of new circumstances that will be more beneficial to you.  \nThis house is also associated with mystery and things hidden deep in our psyche. Therefore, you may face internal fears and depression. This transit gives you the ideal opportunity to think about the psychological blocks you have in yourself and find ways to deal with them.  \nYou will tend to be secretive, and you may need more privacy and time to contemplate. You may also become more interested in astrology, spirituality and occult sciences. You will also focus more on your sexuality. \nThis transit may reveal information that has been hidden to you until now. So, if someone is deceiving you or lying to you, it is likely that you will find out. You also may have to deal with issues of shared finances, taxes, debts and inheritance.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260525T144500Z
DTEND:20260525T144500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165714Z
UID:30_tr_su_sq_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun trine Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Gemini 5°03’) - trine - Natal Pluto \nYour concentration will improve, and you will be driven by your desire for power. It is an ideal time for financial matters and to explore things in depth.  \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 8th house: \nIt’s time for changes! This transit brings with it a profound transformation and it will shine light on everything hidden.  \nIf you are not satisfied with any aspect of life, it is the ideal time to reflect on it and get rid of things that are not for your benefit. It can be people who influence you, your negative qualities and habits, or material things. This transformation is necessary and will provide space for the emergence of new circumstances that will be more beneficial to you.  \nThis house is also associated with mystery and things hidden deep in our psyche. Therefore, you may face internal fears and depression. This transit gives you the ideal opportunity to think about the psychological blocks you have in yourself and find ways to deal with them.  \nYou will tend to be secretive, and you may need more privacy and time to contemplate. You may also become more interested in astrology, spirituality and occult sciences. You will also focus more on your sexuality. \nThis transit may reveal information that has been hidden to you until now. So, if someone is deceiving you or lying to you, it is likely that you will find out. You also may have to deal with issues of shared finances, taxes, debts and inheritance.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
